The input data files are stored in the data-original folder.  This can stored somewhere else with a simlink here or stored locally with the specified subdirectory tree.  Similarly, large intermediate files can be produced from ARQMath-3 code into the prepro_2022 directory which could also be a simlink.

ln -s LOCATION data-original
ln -s LOCATION prepro_2022

mkdir data-original
mkdir data-original/Collection
mkdir data-original/Formulas
mkdir data-original/Thread_Files
mkdir data-original/Task1
mkdir data-original/Task2


These folders should store the MathStackExchange (MSE) data used in ARQMath.  The instruction to download the files can be found from the official ARQMath page.
*Note that "V1.0" is also used for the Comment file, which is an older version.

- data-original/Collection/Badges.V1.2.xml  (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/Comments.V1.0.xml
- data-original/Collection/Comments.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/PostLinks.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/Posts.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/Tags.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/Users.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Collection/Votes.V1.2.xml (or V1.3 in ARQMath-3)

- data-original/Formulas/latex_representation_v2 (folder)  (or _v3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Formulas/slt_representation_v2 (folder) (or _v3 in ARQMath-3)
- data-original/Formulas/opt_representation_v2 (folder) (or _v3 in ARQMath-3)

- data-original/Thread_Files/Collection_By_Year (folder)

- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2020/Topics/Topics_V2.0.xml
- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2020/Topics/Formula_topics_latex_V2.0.tsv
- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2020/Topics/Formula_topics_slt_V2.0.tsv

- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2021/Topics/Topics_Task1_2021_V1.1.xml
- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2021/Topics/Topics_2021_Formulas_Latex_V1.1.tsv
- data-original/Task1/ARQMath-2021/Topics/Topics_2021_Formulas_SLT_V1.1.tsv

- data-original/Task2/ARQMath-2020/Topics/Topics_V1.1.xml

- data-original/Task2/ARQMath-2020/Topics/Topics_Task2_2021_V1.1.xml
